Package: distkv-wago
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends},
  distkv,
  python3-asyncwago,
Replaces: python3-distwago, distkw-wago
Conflicts: python3-distwago, distkw-wago
Provides: python3-distwago, distkw-wago
Description: A distributed no-master key-value store
 DistWAGO is a link between Wago controllers DistKV.
 .
 It will add all discovered Wago ports, monitor them as specified,
 write values that it reads from the controller to some DistKV entry, monitor a
 DistKV entry and write any updates to a controller, and work with DistKV's runner
 system, either centrally or distributed.
